{
  "text": "The R2*, MT, PD* and R1 quantitative maps were calculated as previously described [CITATION_1] . For map calculation we used in-house software running under SPM12 (Wellcome Trust Centre for Neuroimaging, London, UK; www.fil.ion.ucl.ac.uk/spm) and",
